    â””â”€â”€ docker build


Scripted Jenkinsfile â€“ Simple Overview
Starts with node {}
Inside node, you can define stage blocks and run commands directly.
Itâ€™s more flexible, but requires you to write logic manually (like conditionals, loops, etc.).
Good for quick or custom workflows.




